{"tid":2001741,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"狠撇愷樂自保　傳羅志祥返《百分百》避難","createTime":"2020-05-04T18:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T19:19:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a532fe8a7cf99fa65733066d629aecd96a1f8e","tid":2001741,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"台灣天王羅志祥（小豬）被前女友周揚青踢爆私生活淫亂，事業一鋪清袋，已在內地結束14天自我隔離的他，如今下一步動向未明。最新消息指，他將於今月在深圳或上海舉行記者會，而之所以地點選擇內地，全因他為了挽回大陸粉絲的心，倘若計劃失敗，就進行「Plan B」即重回「娘家」他主持約19年的台灣節目《娛樂百分百》。<br />\n<br />\n據知，小豬與「小三」兼旗下藝人愷樂即將完約，兩人合作足足六年，如今合約就到期亦讓小豬可光明正大與愷樂割席，不會造成賠償金的問題，撇清關係自保。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，成功報復的周揚青近日不時在社交網更新，今日她上載一張酒店的Welcome Card，卡上寫有「Sanya（三亞）」字眼，疑似目前在三亞度假。另一張與好友合照中，她頭戴卡通髮箍，狂擺甫士，手舉V字手勢，似乎已經回復好心情！之後佢更上載一條跳舞片，片中用到嘅歌就係佢曾與小豬一齊合跳過嘅，今次真係物事人非喇&hellip;"},{"pid":"6b7257d6e3eb06012c49c3909cdf1feb0c2ed5f3","tid":2001741,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T18:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200504/photo/bkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200504175700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200504175700&h=8476c01d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94829dea5233457985cb96d303c9038c78945156","tid":2001741,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T18:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200504/photo/bkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200504175700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200504175700&h=dc686935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有傳小豬（中）深圳或上海舉行記者會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200504/photo/bkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_03b.jpg?20200504175700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20200504175700&h=b1a959b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愷樂就陰公喇，人同事業都可能冇晒&hellip;"},{"pid":"be98748a2e75a93681e18fbaf8fe004015399a53","tid":2001741,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T18:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200504/photo/bkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_04p.jpg?20200504175700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20200504175700&h=6c553b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周揚青就飛咗去三亞，真係爽YY！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200504/photo/bkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_05p.jpg?20200504175700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20200504175700&h=ed705e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200504/photo/bkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_06p.jpg?20200504175700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200504%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200504165436561-0504_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20200504175700&h=b56ef76a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d8f76e3312dfed6f88234bb42489365f7b3a2c3","tid":2001741,"uid":88982,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"蝴蝶姐姐RAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7778d54b9adb38c7da5f43629b630bbfe4b35e","tid":2001741,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T18:54:51.000Z","msg":"同一個節目做左十九年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas